					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Okay&#8230; As I'm reading it, with still-limited knowledge of the SCPs post-Great Edit (Need to get around to reading the entries more fully), the implication seems to be</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Hide&nbsp;Spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>That humans aren't native to Earth. That either SoI-006 was hunting us or hauling us around, until we managed to kill them, or else they were the original Earth natives until we offed them and took over. Either would be something worth hiding, especially in the particular canon this comes from.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
