						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Without&nbsp;revealing&nbsp;too&nbsp;much...</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Without&nbsp;revealing&nbsp;too&nbsp;much...</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>The spirals aren't connected to the Venusians in any form (that's more of a teaser for a later project I have planned, which ties into 1694), but you are correct about the spirals signifying Pattern Screamers.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
