						 <p>Here's my first go at doing an explained SCP. Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2303803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536632027" alt="Cyantreuse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2303803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" >Cyantreuse</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3213383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536632027" alt="OthellotheCat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3213383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" >OthellotheCat</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536632027" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536632027" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3027978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536632027" alt="mlister" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3027978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/m